---
title: BeaconLink Workflow Execution Sequence
---

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as Platform Operator
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Workflow as Workflow Engine
    participant Planner as Deployment Planner
    participant Scheduler as Distributed Scheduler
    participant Policy as Policy Engine
    participant Inventory as Inventory Service
    participant Relay as Relay Network
    participant Agent as BeaconLink Agent
    participant Runtime as Runtime Manager
    participant Events as Event Streaming Platform
    participant Audit as Audit Service

    %% =====================================================
    %% Workflow Initialization
    %% =====================================================

    User->>API: Submit workflow request

    API->>Workflow: Create workflow instance

    Workflow->>Workflow: Generate Workflow ID
    Workflow->>Workflow: Persist execution state
    Workflow->>Audit: Record workflow creation

    %% =====================================================
    %% Planning Phase
    %% =====================================================

    Workflow->>Planner: Generate execution plan

    Planner->>Inventory: Retrieve infrastructure inventory
    Inventory-->>Planner: Sites, agents, capabilities

    Planner->>Policy: Validate execution constraints
    Policy-->>Planner: Constraints satisfied

    Planner->>Planner: Resolve dependencies
    Planner->>Planner: Build execution graph
    Planner->>Planner: Generate execution stages

    Planner-->>Workflow: Immutable execution plan

    %% =====================================================
    %% Scheduling Phase
    %% =====================================================

    Workflow->>Scheduler: Allocate execution targets

    Scheduler->>Inventory: Discover healthy agents
    Inventory-->>Scheduler: Available execution nodes

    Scheduler->>Scheduler: Evaluate capacity
    Scheduler->>Scheduler: Balance workload
    Scheduler->>Scheduler: Select execution targets

    Scheduler-->>Workflow: Target assignments

    %% =====================================================
    %% Stage Execution
    %% =====================================================

    loop For Each Execution Stage

        Workflow->>Events: Publish StageStarted

        par Parallel Task Execution

            Workflow->>Relay: Dispatch task to Agent A
            Relay->>Agent: Execute task
            Agent->>Runtime: Execute operation
            Runtime-->>Agent: Status

        and

            Workflow->>Relay: Dispatch task to Agent B
            Relay->>Agent: Execute task
            Agent->>Runtime: Execute operation
            Runtime-->>Agent: Status

        and

            Workflow->>Relay: Dispatch task to Agent C
            Relay->>Agent: Execute task
            Agent->>Runtime: Execute operation
            Runtime-->>Agent: Status

        end

        Agent->>Relay: Task completion
        Relay->>Workflow: Aggregate execution results

        Workflow->>Workflow: Verify stage completion

        Workflow->>Events: Publish StageCompleted

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Progress Monitoring
    %% =====================================================

    loop Until Workflow Completes

        Workflow->>Agent: Request execution status

        Agent-->>Workflow: Progress update

        Workflow->>Events: Publish WorkflowProgress

        Workflow->>Audit: Record execution checkpoint

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure Recovery
    %% =====================================================

    alt Task Failure

        Agent-->>Workflow: Execution failed

        Workflow->>Planner: Determine recovery strategy

        alt Retry Allowed

            Planner-->>Workflow: Retry operation

            Workflow->>Relay: Redispatch task

        else Rollback Required

            Planner-->>Workflow: Rollback workflow

            Workflow->>Relay: Execute rollback

            Workflow->>Events: Publish WorkflowRollbackStarted

        end

    else All Tasks Successful

        Workflow->>Events: Publish WorkflowCompleted

        Workflow->>Audit: Record successful execution

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Finalization
    %% =====================================================

    Workflow->>Inventory: Synchronize final state

    Inventory-->>Workflow: State updated

    Workflow-->>API: Workflow completed

    API-->>User: Execution results

    %% =====================================================
    %% Continuous Reconciliation
    %% =====================================================

    Note over Workflow,Agent: After workflow completion,<br/>Continuous Reconciliation ensures the<br/>deployed infrastructure remains aligned<br/>with the immutable Desired State.